svg.title: A floor plan on the left shows twelve unlabeled rooms around a central staircase. There are windows at the front and back. A line indicates 72 feet form front to back. An additional 16 feet of space is indicated at the back, with a small area labeled as a vault. A floor plan on the right shows eight rooms around a central staircase. The four rooms on the left are labeled: a kitchen, two bedrooms, and a sitting room.
